def forward(self, x: torch.Tensor):
        def T(w):
            return w.T if self.fan_in_fan_out else w
        result = F.linear(x, T(self.weight), self.bias)
        if self.r > 0:
            x_d = self.lora_dropout(x)
            # SVD-based adaptation: (x @ Q^T * Λ) @ P^T
            # lora_A: (r, in_features), lora_E: (r, 1), lora_B: (out_features, r)
            # x_d: (batch, in_features)
            # (x_d @ lora_A.T): (batch, r)
            # (x_d @ lora_A.T) * lora_E.T: (batch, r)
            # ((x_d @ lora_A.T) * lora_E.T) @ lora_B.T: (batch, out_features)
            svd_update = ((x_d @ self.lora_A.T) * self.lora_E.T) @ self.lora_B.T
            result = result + svd_update * self.scaling / (self.ranknum + 1e-5)
        return result
